{"chapter_number":83,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":86,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"المطففين","name_complex":"Al-Muţaffifīn","name_simple":"Al-Mutaffifin","verses_count":36,"pages":[587,589],"meaning":{"text":"The Defrauding","en":"The Defrauding","id":"Orang-orang Curang"},"verses":[[[1,5849,"83:1","وَيْلٌ لِّلْمُطَفِّفِينَ",["Woe to the defrauders,","Celakalah bagi orang-orang yang curang (dalam menakar dan menimbang)!"],587,30,59,235,null,null],[2,5850,"83:2","الَّذِينَ إِذَا اكْتَالُوا عَلَى النَّاسِ يَسْتَوْفُونَ",["Who, when they take the measure (of their dues) from men take it fully,","(Yaitu) orang-orang yang apabila menerima takaran dari orang lain mereka minta dicukupkan,"],587,30,59,235,null,null],[3,5851,"83:3","وَإِذَا كَالُوهُمْ أَو وَّزَنُوهُمْ يُخْسِرُونَ",["But when they measure out to others or weigh out for them, they are deficient.","dan apabila mereka menakar atau menimbang (untuk orang lain), mereka mengurangi."],587,30,59,235,null,null],[4,5852,"83:4","أَلَا يَظُنُّ أُولَٰئِكَ أَنَّهُم مَّبْعُوثُونَ",["Do not these think that they shall be raised again","Tidakkah mereka itu mengira, bahwa sesungguhnya mereka akan dibangkitkan,"],587,30,59,235,null,null],[5,5853,"83:5","لِيَوْمٍ عَظِيمٍ",["For a mighty day,","pada suatu hari yang besar,"],587,30,59,235,null,null],[6,5854,"83:6","يَوْمَ يَقُومُ النَّاسُ لِرَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ",["The day on which men shall stand before the Lord of the worlds?","(yaitu) pada hari (ketika) semua orang bangkit menghadap Tuhan seluruh alam."],587,30,59,235,null,null],[7,5855,"83:7","كَلَّا إِنَّ كِتَابَ الْفُجَّارِ لَفِي سِجِّينٍ",["Nay! most surely the record of the wicked is in the Sijjin.","Sekali-kali jangan begitu! Sesungguhnya catatan orang yang durhaka benar-benar tersimpan dalam Sijjn."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[8,5856,"83:8","وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا سِجِّينٌ",["And what will make you know what the Sijjin is?","Dan tahukah engkau apakah Sijjn itu?"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[9,5857,"83:9","كِتَابٌ مَّرْقُومٌ",["It is a written book.","(Yaitu) Kitab yang berisi catatan (amal)."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[10,5858,"83:10","وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",["Woe on that day to the rejecters,","Celakalah pada hari itu, bagi orang-orang yang mendustakan!"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[11,5859,"83:11","الَّذِينَ يُكَذِّبُونَ بِيَوْمِ الدِّينِ",["Who give the lie to the day of judgment.","(yaitu) orang-orang yang mendustakannya (hari pembalasan)."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[12,5860,"83:12","وَمَا يُكَذِّبُ بِهِ إِلَّا كُلُّ مُعْتَدٍ أَثِيمٍ",["And none gives the lie to it but every exceeder of limits, sinful one","Dan tidak ada yang mendustakannya (hari pembalasan) kecuali setiap orang yang melampaui batas dan berdosa,"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[13,5861,"83:13","إِذَا تُتْلَىٰ عَلَيْهِ آيَاتُنَا قَالَ أَسَاطِيرُ الْأَوَّلِينَ",["When Our communications are recited to him, he says: Stories of those of yore.","yang apabila dibacakan kepadanya ayat-ayat Kami, dia berkata, “Itu adalah dongeng orang-orang dahulu.”"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[14,5862,"83:14","كَلَّا ۖ بَلْ ۜ رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِم مَّا كَانُوا يَكْسِبُونَ",["Nay! rather, what they used to do has become like rust upon their hearts.","Sekali-kali tidak! Bahkan apa yang mereka kerjakan itu telah menutupi hati mereka."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[15,5863,"83:15","كَلَّا إِنَّهُمْ عَن رَّبِّهِمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ لَّمَحْجُوبُونَ",["Nay! most surely they shall on that day be debarred from their Lord.","Sekali-kali tidak! Sesungguhnya mereka pada hari itu benar-benar terhalang dari (melihat) Tuhannya."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[16,5864,"83:16","ثُمَّ إِنَّهُمْ لَصَالُو الْجَحِيمِ",["Then most surely they shall enter the burning fire.","Kemudian, sesungguhnya mereka benar-benar masuk neraka."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[17,5865,"83:17","ثُمَّ يُقَالُ هَٰذَا الَّذِي كُنتُم بِهِ تُكَذِّبُونَ",["Then shall it be said: This is what you gave the lie to.","Kemudian, dikatakan (kepada mereka), “Inilah (azab) yang dahulu kamu dustakan.”"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[18,5866,"83:18","كَلَّا إِنَّ كِتَابَ الْأَبْرَارِ لَفِي عِلِّيِّينَ",["Nay! Most surely the record of the righteous shall be in the Iliyin.","Sekali-kali tidak! Sesungguhnya catatan orang-orang yang berbakti benar-benar tersimpan dalam ’Illiyyn."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[19,5867,"83:19","وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا عِلِّيُّونَ",["And what will make you know what the highest Iliyin is?","Dan tahukah engkau apakah ’Illiyyn itu?"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[20,5868,"83:20","كِتَابٌ مَّرْقُومٌ",["It is a written book,","(Yaitu) Kitab yang berisi catatan (amal),"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[21,5869,"83:21","يَشْهَدُهُ الْمُقَرَّبُونَ",["Those who are drawn near (to Allah) shall witness it.","yang disaksikan oleh (malaikat-malaikat) yang didekatkan (kepada Allah)."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[22,5870,"83:22","إِنَّ الْأَبْرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٍ",["Most surely the righteous shall be in bliss,","Sesungguhnya orang-orang yang berbakti benar-benar berada dalam (surga yang penuh) kenikmatan,"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[23,5871,"83:23","عَلَى الْأَرَائِكِ يَنظُرُونَ",["On thrones, they shall gaze;","mereka (duduk) di atas dipan-dipan melepas pandangan"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[24,5872,"83:24","تَعْرِفُ فِي وُجُوهِهِمْ نَضْرَةَ النَّعِيمِ",["You will recognize in their faces the brightness of bliss.","Kamu dapat mengetahui dari wajah mereka kesenangan hidup yang penuh kenikmatan."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[25,5873,"83:25","يُسْقَوْنَ مِن رَّحِيقٍ مَّخْتُومٍ",["They are made to quaff of a pure drink that is sealed (to others).","Mereka diberi minum dari khamar murni (tidak memabukkan) yang (tempatnya) masih dilak (disegel),"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[26,5874,"83:26","خِتَامُهُ مِسْكٌ ۚ وَفِي ذَٰلِكَ فَلْيَتَنَافَسِ الْمُتَنَافِسُونَ",["The sealing of it is (with) musk; and for that let the aspirers aspire.","laknya dari kasturi. Dan untuk yang demikian itu hendaknya orang berlomba-lomba."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[27,5875,"83:27","وَمِزَاجُهُ مِن تَسْنِيمٍ",["And the admixture of it is a water of Tasnim,","Dan campurannya dari tasnm,"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[28,5876,"83:28","عَيْنًا يَشْرَبُ بِهَا الْمُقَرَّبُونَ",["A fountain from which drink they who are drawn near (to Allah).","(yaitu) mata air yang diminum oleh mereka yang dekat (kepada Allah)."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[29,5877,"83:29","إِنَّ الَّذِينَ أَجْرَمُوا كَانُوا مِنَ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا يَضْحَكُونَ",["Surely they who are guilty used to laugh at those who believe.","Sesungguhnya orang-orang yang berdosa adalah mereka yang dahulu menertawakan orang-orang yang beriman."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[30,5878,"83:30","وَإِذَا مَرُّوا بِهِمْ يَتَغَامَزُونَ",["And when they passed by them, they winked at one another.","Dan apabila mereka (orang-orang yang beriman) melintas di hadapan mereka, mereka saling mengedip-ngedipkan matanya,"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[31,5879,"83:31","وَإِذَا انقَلَبُوا إِلَىٰ أَهْلِهِمُ انقَلَبُوا فَكِهِينَ",["And when they returned to their own followers they returned exulting.","dan apabila kembali kepada kaumnya, mereka kembali dengan gembira ria."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[32,5880,"83:32","وَإِذَا رَأَوْهُمْ قَالُوا إِنَّ هَٰؤُلَاءِ لَضَالُّونَ",["And when they saw them, they said: Most surely these are in error;","Dan apabila mereka melihat (orang-orang mukmin), mereka mengatakan, “Sesungguhnya mereka benar-benar orang-orang sesat,”"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[33,5881,"83:33","وَمَا أُرْسِلُوا عَلَيْهِمْ حَافِظِينَ",["And they were not sent to be keepers over them.","padahal (orang-orang yang berdosa itu), mereka tidak diutus sebagai penjaga (orang-orang mukmin)."],588,30,59,235,null,null],[34,5882,"83:34","فَالْيَوْمَ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا مِنَ الْكُفَّارِ يَضْحَكُونَ",["So today those who believe shall laugh at the unbelievers;","Maka pada hari ini, orang-orang yang beriman yang menertawakan orang-orang kafir,"],588,30,59,235,null,null],[35,5883,"83:35","عَلَى الْأَرَائِكِ يَنظُرُونَ",["On thrones, they will look.","mereka (duduk) di atas dipan-dipan melepas pandangan."],589,30,59,235,null,null],[36,5884,"83:36","هَلْ ثُوِّبَ الْكُفَّارُ مَا كَانُوا يَفْعَلُونَ",["Surely the disbelievers are rewarded as they did.","Apakah orang-orang kafir itu diberi balasan (hukuman) terhadap apa yang telah mereka perbuat?"],589,30,59,235,null,null]],[[[1,13,587,"&#xfbd6;","word","وَيْلٌ",["Woe",""]],[2,13,587,"&#xfbd7;","word","لِلْمُطَفِّفِينَ",["to those who give less",""]],[3,13,587,"&#xfbd8;","end","ﯘ",[null,null]]],[[1,13,587,"&#xfbd9;","word","الَّذِينَ",["Those who","orang-orang yang"]],[2,13,587,"&#xfbda;","word","إِذَا",["when","apabila"]],[3,13,587,"&#xfbdb;","word","اكْتَالُوا",["they take a measure","mereka menerima takaran"]],[4,13,587,"&#xfbdc;","word","عَلَى",["from","atas"]],[5,13,587,"&#xfbdd;","word","النَّاسِ",["the people","manusia (orang lain)"]],[6,13,587,"&#xfbde;","word","يَسْتَوْفُونَ",["they take in full","mereka minta dipenuhi"]],[7,13,587,"&#xfbdf;","end","ﯟ",[null,null]]],[[1,14,587,"&#xfbe0;","word","وَإِذَا",["But when","dan apabila"]],[2,14,587,"&#xfbe1;","word","كَالُوهُمْ",["they give by measure (to) them","mereka menakar"]],[3,14,587,"&#xfbe2;","word","أَوْ",["or","atau"]],[4,14,587,"&#xfbe3;","word","وَزَنُوهُمْ",["they weigh (for) them","mereka menimbang"]],[5,14,587,"&#xfbe4;","word","يُخْسِرُونَ",["they give less","mengurangi"]],[6,14,587,"&#xfbe5;","end","ﯥ",[null,null]]],[[1,14,587,"&#xfbe6;","word","أَلَا",["Do not","tidakkah"]],[2,14,587,"&#xfbe7;","word","يَظُنُّ",["think","mereka menyangka"]],[3,14,587,"&#xfbe8;","word","أُولَٰئِكَ",["those","mereka itu"]],[4,14,587,"&#xfbe9;","word","أَنَّهُمْ",["that they","bahwa sesungguhnya mereka"]],[5,15,587,"&#xfbea;","word","مَبْعُوثُونَ",["(will be) resurrected","orang-orang yang dibangkitkan"]],[6,15,587,"&#xfbeb;","end","ﯫ",[null,null]]],[[1,15,587,"&#xfbec;","word","لِيَوْمٍ",["For a Day","pada hari"]],[2,15,587,"&#xfbed;","word","عَظِيمٍ",["Great","yang besar"]],[3,15,587,"&#xfbee;","end","ﯮ",[null